{"comments":"Section view and hatching primitives for engineering drawings.\n\n## What are Section Views?\n\nSection views show internal features by \"cutting\" through an object:\n\n- **Full section**: Cut completely through\n- **Half section**: Cut halfway (symmetrical parts)\n- **Offset section**: Cut plane changes direction\n- **Broken-out section**: Local cutaway\n- **Revolved section**: Cross-section rotated into view\n\n## Hatching\n\nCross-hatching indicates cut surfaces:\n\n- **Material hatching**: Different patterns for different materials\n- **Part hatching**: Adjacent parts have different angles\n- **Assembly hatching**: Components distinguished by pattern\n\n## Standards\n\n- **ASME Y14.3**: Multi-view and sectional view drawings\n- **ISO 128**: Technical drawings — general principles\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[111,16],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Engineering/Section.purs","start":[111,3]},"title":"FullSection"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[112,16],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Engineering/Section.purs","start":[112,3]},"title":"HalfSection"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[113,18],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Engineering/Section.purs","start":[113,3]},"title":"OffsetSection"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[114,21],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Engineering/Section.purs","start":[114,3]},"title":"BrokenOutSection"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[115,20],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Engineering/Section.purs","start":[115,3]},"title":"RevolvedSection"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[116,19],"name":".